      • copyAndSet

        public final AColGroup copyAndSet​(IDictionary newDictionary)

        Parameters:

      • reduceCols

        public AColGroup reduceCols()
        Description copied from class: AColGroup

        Specified by:
        reduceCols in class AColGroup
